{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "57b21ed4-76e4-48be-b4b3-dc5ac9b21cda", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/57b21ed4-76e4-48be-b4b3-dc5ac9b21cda@1.pkg/1772597696469/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597697029", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/57b21ed4-76e4-48be-b4b3-dc5ac9b21cda@1.pkg/1772597696469/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597697029"}, "identifier": "57b21ed4-76e4-48be-b4b3-dc5ac9b21cda", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查掌握交友的基本原则。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①：&ldquo;交友投分，切磨箴规&rdquo;意思是要结交志趣相投，能在学习上相互切磋的朋友，符合题意。故①正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>②：&ldquo;功崇惟志，业广惟勤&rdquo;强调成就功业源于志向高远，拓展事业依靠勤奋不懈。与题目要求的&ldquo;对交友有启示作用&rdquo;无关，故②错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>③：&ldquo;与君远相知，不道云海深&rdquo;主要表达的是对朋友的思念之情，并未提到交友的原则和启示，与题目中强调&ldquo;对交友有启示作用&rdquo;无关，因此③错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>④：&ldquo;君子以文会友，以友辅仁&rdquo;意思是通过学问交流结交朋友，借助朋友辅助培养仁德。符合题意。因此④正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①④正确，因此选B</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）友谊是人生永恒的话题，伴随着我们的成长。下列古语对我们交友有启示作用的是（　　　）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①交友投分，切磨箴规 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②功崇惟志，业广惟勤&rdquo;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③与君远相知，不道云海深 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④君子以文会友，以友辅仁</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）友谊是人生永恒的话题，伴随着我们的成长。下列古语对我们交友有启示作用的是（　　　）①交友投分，切磨箴规         ②功崇惟志，业广惟勤”③与君远相知，不道云海深     ④君子以文会友，以友辅仁", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/57b21ed4-76e4-48be-b4b3-dc5ac9b21cda@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977940355", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①② &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①④ &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②④ &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③④</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: j